snippet.title: La Linea - GameBoy Homebrew
snippet.description:
Based on an Italian cartoon of the same name, this is an original Game Boy homebrew game developed by Rajcsányi László (WLS), created using the popular GB Studio.

Download the game from his website: https://www.wls.hu/

#retrogames #retrogaming #wls #gameboy #gb #gameboyhomebrew #gbhomebrew #itchio #gbstudio
